p: ONNV strain SG650 and Zika virus strain FSS13025 were obtained from the University of Texas Medical Branch World Reference Center for Emerging Viruses and Arboviruses. Stocks were generated by inoculating Vero cells (ONNV) or C6/36 cells (ZIKV). All virus stocks were stored at –80°C and titered on Vero or C6/36 cells.
